7522:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
7523:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7524:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
7525:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV4: ETRP frequency divided by 4.
7526:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV8: ETRP frequency divided by 8.
7527:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  TIM_ExtTRGPolarity The external Trigger Polarity.
7528:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
7529:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_INVERTED: active low or falling edge active.
7530:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPOLARITY_NONINVERTED: active high or rising edge active.
7531:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  ExtTRGFilter External Trigger Filter.
7532:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter must be a value between 0x00 and 0x0F
7533:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @retval None
7534:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   */
